<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/298902-shouldn-t-this-book-be-a-bestseller">Shouldn&#39;t this book be a bestseller?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_298902'><a id="like_count_community_question_298902" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/298902?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">42 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F890.Of_Mice_and_Men">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/298902-shouldn-t-this-book-be-a-bestseller">7 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/298902-shouldn-t-this-book-be-a-bestseller">See all 7 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

