<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I think he does it mostly for loneliness. Lennie is a friend that adores him and would never betray him, and this is a treasure not many people have, <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I think he does it mostly for loneliness. Lennie is a friend that adores him and would never betray him, and this is a treasure not many people have, especially among vagrants.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
