        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer588657421" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5309772561107981963"><i>Of Mice and Men</i> is a tale about the ultimate kindness - it is hard to talk about kindness without turning sentimental but <b>John Steinbeck</b> was the one who really could.<br/><blockquote>His ear heard more than what was said to him, and his slow speech had overtones not of thought, but of understanding beyond thought.</blockquote><br/>Simple men of this cruel world live in their own dreamlands and they dream of rainbows.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


