        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1758253665" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10496035540162239179">I often think of this book when I see mentally ill people on the streets. I must admit that I am jealous of John Steinbeck...what I would not give to be able to write 1/4 as well as he could. One of the books that made me fall in love with the classics.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


